==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Miscalculate
<hw>Mis*cal"cu*late</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t. & i.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>To calculate erroneously.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To judge wrongly, especially about the effects of
action or the likely course of events.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>miscalculation</ent>⟦br⟧
